Package: Rgtk4
Type: Package
Title: R Bindings for GTK4
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jan Marvin", "Garbuszus", email = "jan.garbuszus@ruhr-uni-bochum.de", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("RGtk2 Team", role = "ctb", comment = "Conceptual foundation and inspiration"))
Description: Complete R bindings for GTK4 (GIMP Toolkit version 4) automatically 
    generated from GObject Introspection metadata. Provides access to GTK4, GLib, 
    GObject, Gio, Pango, GdkPixbuf, and Cairo libraries with meaningful parameter 
    names, platform-specific function filtering, and native R event loop integration.
    Includes macOS-specific integrations for dock icon management and keyboard shortcuts.
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: GTK4 (>= 4.0.0), GObject-Introspection (>= 1.0.0), pkg-config
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: utils
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    later,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/JanMarvin/Rgtk4
BugReports: https://github.com/JanMarvin/Rgtk4/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
